            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b509a8995f60ddd9-f09fcd twpub-b509a8995f60ddd9-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 3.  Information about the Project Gutenberg Literary Archive\nFoundation</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b509a8995f60ddd9/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b509a8995f60ddd9/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b509a8995f60ddd9-f09fcd twpub-b509a8995f60ddd9-6b4cd0\"><p>The Project Gutenberg Literary Archive Foundation is a non profit\n501(c)(3) educational corporation organized under the laws of the\nstate of Mississippi and granted tax exempt status by the Internal\nRevenue Service.  The Foundation's EIN or federal tax identification\nnumber is 64-6221541.  Its 501(c)(3) letter is posted at\nhttp://pglaf.org/fundraising.  Contributions to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation are tax deductible to the full extent\npermitted by U.S. federal laws and your state's laws.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b509a8995f60ddd9/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b509a8995f60ddd9/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b509a8995f60ddd9-f09fcd twpub-b509a8995f60ddd9-6b4cd0\"><p>The Foundation's principal office is located at 4557 Melan Dr. S.\nFairbanks, AK, 99712., but its volunteers and employees are scattered\nthroughout numerous locations.  Its business office is located at\n809 North 1500 West, Salt Lake City, UT 84116, (801) 596-1887, email\nbusiness@pglaf.org.  Email contact links and up to date contact\ninformation can be found at the Foundation's web site and official\npage at http://pglaf.org</p></div>"
        },
